OL,5, A deaf teaching assistant is to work   
OL,6, with a deaf pupil for the first time in
OL,7, a mainstream school in Wales.          
OL,9,FEmma Day, 21, said she felt proud to   
OL,10,Fhave been appointed at Ysgol Clydau in 
OL,11,FTegryn, Pembrokeshire.                 
OL,13,FThere she will work with 11-year-old   
OL,14,FEvelyn who also has lessons translated 
OL,15,Fby British Sign Language interpreters. 
OL,17,F"The most rewarding thing is seeing    
OL,18,FEvelyn's confidence grow and how she   
OL,19,Fenjoys learning through her first      
OL,20,Flanguage, sign language," Emma said.   
